               <provenance>The name Gabra Mikāʾel is written in the main
                     hand in the supplication formulas, e.g., 1ra,
                     22va, 34va, 64vb. Many other names are also written in the supplication
                     formulas in the main hand: Gabra Mikāʾel (e.g., 1ra, 13ra, 22va, 34va, 56ra, 64vb), ʾAklilä Māryām (27rb, 55vb, 56va, 63rb), Śahlä Mikāʾel (28vb), Walatta Giyorgis (36rb, 48vb, 54va, 63rb), Walatta Ḥǝywat (37ra).</provenance></history>
